      <h1>Combining registers</h1>
      <p>You can easily combine data from one register with data from another. This can help if you need access to data from more than one organisation to build your service.</p> 

      <p>For example, you might need to use data from the country register as well as the territory register to build a feature in your service that users can use to find their location.</p>
